Molly Price https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Molly_Price 0 Molly Evan Price (born December 15, 1965) is an American actress. She is best known for her role as Faith Yokas in the NBC drama series Third Watch (1999-2005). Price also has appeared in a recurring and guest starring roles in many other television dramas and co-starred in a number of films, include Sweet and Lowdown (1999), Chasing Sleep (2000), and Not Fade Away (2012).
